title: Episode 77: Kranium
itunes:title: Episode 77: Kranium
description:
This week, Angela Yee, Stephanie Santiago and Gigi Maguire's travel to Atlantic records to kick it with reggae artist Kranium. They discuss tips on how to get away with cheating, how much a person's diet matters when you are dating, how long it takes for the newness of relationships to wear out, and buying gifts for new boos on Christmas.
